before I was smart.

967
00:54:01,880 --> 00:54:03,233
Mr. Pollard, are you...

968
00:54:03,400 --> 00:54:06,119
the natural father
of Mary Adler?

969
00:54:06,280 --> 00:54:07,759
Yes, I am.

970
00:54:07,920 --> 00:54:09,478
And how can you be
certain of this?

971
00:54:09,960 --> 00:54:13,077
Well, I always knew,
but then you had me...

972
00:54:13,240 --> 00:54:14,719
