I have a job of my own.

985
00:54:44,760 --> 00:54:45,760
Thank you.

986
00:54:45,840 --> 00:54:47,512
No further questions,
Your Honor.

987
00:54:47,720 --> 00:54:48,835
Mr. Pollard...

988
00:54:49,000 --> 00:54:51,355
when was the last time
