1044
00:57:29,720 --> 00:57:32,917
He has a cowboy hat
and cowboy boots...

1045
00:57:33,080 --> 00:57:35,355
and a horse
that doesn't know dressage.

1046
00:57:35,520 --> 00:57:37,272
