1121
01:03:47,840 --> 01:03:49,751
You know baseball.

1122
01:03:49,920 --> 01:03:50,920
Fenway Park.

1123
01:03:51,000 --> 01:03:52,600
You know, I'd like to go there
some time.

1124
01:03:53,000 --> 01:03:55,116
How often in a year

1125
01:03:55,200 --> 01:03:56,838
